<div class="title">Dillusions</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines - Dexamphetamine Sulphate</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Indigo&Exact=1">Indigo</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Indigo. "Dillusions: An Experience with Amphetamines - Dexamphetamine Sulphate (exp34239)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 8, 2004. erowid.org/exp/34239</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
